  <h2>Our Commitment to Transparency</h2>
  <p>At AI Tools Idea, we believe you deserve to know exactly how we make money and whether it affects what we write. This page explains our affiliate relationships clearly and completely.</p>

  <hr />

  <h2>What Is an Affiliate Link?</h2>
  <p>An <strong>affiliate link</strong> is a special URL that tracks whether you arrived at a product's website through our link. If you then sign up for a paid plan or make a purchase, the company pays us a commission — at <strong>no extra cost to you</strong>.</p>
  <p>The price you pay is identical whether you click our link or go directly to the company's website.</p>

  <hr />

